    "causal_summary": "Phase 001 is the substrate child of the Gem Team adoption work in 027. The phase-007 study (19 iterations) and the phase-009 integration synthesis (5 iterations) converged on one finding: the spec-kit's agents already carry rich, evidence-first contracts, but the orchestration-relevant facts (status, confidence, failure class, dispatch intent) are expressed in scattered prose and are not machine-parseable. This packet adds a typed, OPTIONAL adapter layer over the existing contracts — never replacing the rich-markdown bodies.",
